#. Max bytes: 43
msgctxt "Offset_0x2E0_Len_43"
msgid "Kiryu-san... Thank you so much for earlier."
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 65
msgctxt "Offset_0x460_Len_65"
msgid "You were so dashing when you stepped in...\nWho could resist that?"
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 55
msgctxt "Offset_0x620_Len_55"
msgid "I know I need to work on being\r\nmore of a girly-girl..."
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 43
msgctxt "Offset_0x7C0_Len_43"
msgid "But today, I'm going to do something brave."
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 36
msgctxt "Offset_0x9E0_Len_36"
msgid "I've always fantasized about this..."
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 24
msgctxt "Offset_0xB70_Len_24"
msgid "Kiryu-san... I love you."
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 36
msgctxt "Offset_0xCE0_Len_36"
msgid "I hope you'll watch over me forever."
msgstr ""

